    "However, it appears that, unlike standard SK, the analysis of QAOA performance is unlikely to lead to significant insights when the weights are biased.",
    "Our observation that QAOA parameters γ have to decrease with problem size is an instantiation of a broader principle, namely that parameterized quantum circuits are not scale-independent.",
